node.text:
m o m e n t s ||
🖤
Feeling a wee bit run down, so I cancelled training this morning to rest and snuggle this one. Learning to read cues, slow down and be kind to myself.
🖤
Life is vibrant, dynamic and sometimes demanding to the point of overwhelm. At these moments I inevitably find myself towards the bottom of “the list”. You know the place right?
🖤
Self love ... it’s not selfish, it’s not “me first”. It’s learning to say “me too”.
It’s checking in with the soul. Reconnecting to your body + mind to tip those scales back to balance.
🖤
Pics from last week. A little walk with this beauty before we launched into our days.
Sun up.
Crisp air.
Much gratitude.
🖤
📷 @tyla_angel11
@colombianyogagirl but dear Cat, it is you who inspire me! 🙊❤️
@magicalrocket 💋💋💋im not worthy ;)! sending you light and BiGLOVE 💖💖💖💖💖💖💖💖💖💖💖💖
Sammy I want to be like you when I grow up 🙉🙈you are perfect.
@fernandaoconnell How good to share so much (wisdom😂, aka as I say not as I do). My greatest joy is watching her bloom. 💫💖
The greatest gift.... to have a little buddy buddy to share life.... to pass on our wisdom 😂 and to nurture and see them flourish into amazing humans..... @magicalrocket
@heidi_robb pure joy 💖 love you gorgeous Heidi.
Look at you two beautiful girks❤️❤️❤️
@beckjstevens hello beautiful mumma 💖✨ enjoy every moment!
